*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT zgy_0018.

PARAMETERS:cb1 AS CHECKBOX,
           cb2 AS CHECKBOX,
           cb3 AS CHECKBOX.
DATA:gv_num    TYPE i VALUE 10.

START-OF-SELECTION.
  IF cb1 EQ abap_true.
    PERFORM 2ekle.
  ENDIF.

  IF cb2 EQ abap_true.
    PERFORM 3ekle.
  ENDIF.

  IF cb3 EQ abap_true.
    PERFORM 5ekle.
  ENDIF.

  WRITE:gv_num.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form 2EKLE
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM 2ekle .
  gv_num = gv_num + 2.
ENDFORM.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form 3EKLE
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM 3ekle .
  gv_num = gv_num + 3.
ENDFORM.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form 5EKLE
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM 5ekle .
  gv_num = gv_num + 5.
ENDFORM.
